# ============================================================================
# _dicom-dump — zsh completion for **dicom-dump** — Enet4/dicom-rs,
#                the canonical Rust workspace's **DICOM file
#                inspector CLI**.  Reads `.dcm` (DICOM Part-10) files
#                — the binary container format used by every CT,
#                MRI, X-ray, fluoroscopy, ultrasound, PET, SPECT,
#                mammography, dental panoramic, ophthalmology
#                (OCT/fundus), nuclear medicine, and radiotherapy
#                planning system on Earth — and pretty-prints every
#                Data Element (`(group,element)` tag pair, VR
#                discriminator, VL length, and decoded value) as
#                either human-readable colorized text or as
#                DICOM-JSON (per the DICOM standard's PS3.18 Annex F
#                JSON encoding).  Rust=174 OPENING leg of new Axis
#                119 (DICOM / NEMA PS3 medical imaging protocol)
#                via the canonical Rust DICOM library workspace
#                **Enet4/dicom-rs** (its `dicom-core` / `dicom-
#                encoding` / `dicom-object` / `dicom-json` /
#                `dicom-dictionary-std` / `dicom-transfer-syntax-
#                registry` family).
